data.title: The Ageyevs from Kosachevka
data.meta_description: Summary report of The Ageyevs from Kosachevka containing 392 individuals and 121 families.  This report describes the genealogy and ancestry of families Ageyev, Ageyeva, Yakovleva, Minin, Lawrence, Sohn, Romanov, Michelenko, Kuper, Ivanova.
